areer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3705, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 503692, "username": "rimworld", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/rimworld", "website": "https://www.duyihao.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "mutuyihao", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_mini.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_normal.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_large.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_xlarge.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_xxlarge.png?m=1781236811", "created": 1597330016, "last_modified": 1781236811, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "konakona", "last_touched": 1783104333, "title": "多年以后，面对前端如此困难的求职环境，你是否还会回想起当初第一次敲下 HTML 的那个遥远的下午", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224814", "created": 1783071691, "deleted": 0, "content": "哎，工作好难找。\r\n打了几千个招呼，就个位数约面，然后走不到终面就没消息了。\r\n最近这家更是不做人了，HR 好友都加不上，面完一周也没消息。在线面试面试官也不开摄像头。\r\n多年以后，面对前端如此困难的求职环境，你是否还会回想起当初第一次敲下 HTML ，听着电脑机箱风扇的噪音，吹着风扇，室友在上铺打着农药的那个遥远的下午。", "content_rendered": "哎，工作好难找。<br />打了几千个招呼，就个位数约面，然后走不到终面就没消息了。<br />最近这家更是不做人了，HR 好友都加不上，面完一周也没消息。在线面试面试官也不开摄像头。<br />多年以后，面对前端如此困难的求职环境，你是否还会回想起当初第一次敲下 HTML ，听着电脑机箱风扇的噪音，吹着风扇，室友在上铺打着农药的那个遥远的下午。", "last_modified": 1783071691, "replies": 26, "id": 1224814}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0690/59b7/126_large.png?m=1371465007", "name": "edu", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0690/59b7/126_normal.png?m=1371465007", "title": "教育", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/edu", "topics": 466, "footer": null, "header": "终身学习", "title_alternative": "Education", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0690/59b7/126_mini.png?m=1371465007", "stars": 94, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 126, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 683571, "username": "Ashe007", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Ashe007", "website": "https://ashe-wiki.github.io/", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cdb3/c329/683571_mini.png?m=1717585814", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cdb3/c329/683571_normal.png?m=1717585814", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cdb3/c329/683571_large.png?m=1717585814", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cdb3/c329/683571_xlarge.png?m=1717585814", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cdb3/c329/683571_xxlarge.png?m=1717585814", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cdb3/c329/683571_xxxlarge.png?m=1717585814", "created": 1712136453, "last_modified": 1717585814, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Ashe007", "last_touched": 1783100836, "title": "v2 不是喜欢推荐高考生选计算机专业吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224832", "created": 1783077636, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://v2ex.com/t/1053452#reply42\r\n\r\n头两年一大堆人推荐高考生选计算机，今年我看 v2 提问建议专业的人少了特别多，回答的也没什么人推荐计算机了，之前还有人说我上车了就像关门，现在想想真是嘲讽啊\r\n\r\n如今 ai 时代，那些在各大论坛上争先恐后地说 AI 替代不了程序员的群体，怎么没在其他话题领域发光发热？有时候真感觉社会舆论在被某些人操控啊", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/1053452#reply42\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://v2ex.com/t/1053452#reply42</a></p>\n<p>头两年一大堆人推荐高考生选计算机，今年我看 v2 提问建议专业的人少了特别多，回答的也没什么人推荐计算机了，之前还有人说我上车了就像关门，现在想想真是嘲讽啊</p>\n<p>如今 ai 时代，那些在各大论坛上争先恐后地说 AI 替代不了程序员的群体，怎么没在其他话题领域发光发热？有时候真感觉社会舆论在被某些人操控啊</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783077636, "replies": 22, "id": 1224832}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 239655, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4497, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 9346, "username": "tinolau", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/tinolau", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a17039a6dc0c3049057fdedf53225add?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a17039a6dc0c3049057fdedf53225add?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a17039a6dc0c3049057fdedf53225add?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1307538756, "last_modified": 1738935972, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "imicksoft", "last_touched": 1783116903, "title": "你希望别人拥有的人生体验", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224838", "created": 1783080987, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近做了一个网站，想收集一些回答。\r\n如果你可以指定陌生人干一件事情，你希望让他做什么（不一定是为你而做）,小到拍一张照片，喝一杯水都行\r\n大家动动发财的小手回复一下", "content_rendered": "<p>最近做了一个网站，想收集一些回答。\n如果你可以指定陌生人干一件事情，你希望让他做什么（不一定是为你而做）,小到拍一张照片，喝一杯水都行\n大家动动发财的小手回复一下</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783128671, "replies": 21, "id": 1224838}]